%% 3.2.12 View Order List — sequence
%% GET /api/Order/Search?guardianId=&status=&...
%% BR59: Newest first — verify OrderService Search ordering

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant OC as OrderController
    participant OS as OrderService
    participant Repo as IRepository Order
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Guardian->>App: Open My Orders / History
    App->>OC: GET /api/Order/Search?guardianId=...&status=...
    OC->>OS: SearchOrderAsync
    OS->>Repo: Query + Include Package, Student
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    OS-->>OC: paged orders (newest first per backend)
    OC-->>App: 200 OK — tabs Pending / Paid / Expired
